Short guide:
----------------------------
1. Go to Pomagalo.com and login with your details. If you aren't registered, please register from the registration link in the Pomagalo's site.
2. Select a document, which you want to download.
3. Under the document viewer will apear a box, from which you can download the document.
4. Select document's data type for download.
5. ... and the document will be downloaded.
6. That's all!